outputs.output_descr:
This project specifically targets geographical areas where resistance to the new Libya has been strong. Although needs exist across many sectors , the project will prioritize initial capacity needs and priority activities in the following areas:
1. Support and develop the capacity of CSOs to provide services and rebuild conflict affected cities;
2. Strengthen capacity of local CSOs in particular on key managerial and technical areas;
3. Strengthen local authorities to prepare local development plans and provide rapid support to the rebuilding of cities in conflict prone areas in order to transition from humanitarian action to early recovery in order to sustain initial humanitarian gains
